{"TopicId":218401,"ForumId":15,"TopicTitle":"Custom BDArmory Modding","CreatedByName":"kerpalmasheen","CreatedById":224450,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-14T00:34:59Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"kerpalmasheen","CreatedById":224450,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-14T00:34:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do I make a 3D model that I can use to make new BDArmory guns/missiles?\u00A0 I have got the code figured out (other than node definitions).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ColdJ","CreatedById":211123,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-16T04:30:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224302280\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022218401\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221689294899\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022224450\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerpalmasheen\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/14/2023 at 10:34 AM, kerpalmasheen said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do I make a 3D model that I can use to make new BDArmory guns/missiles?\u00A0 I have got the code figured out (other than node definitions).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf it is the 3D modelling side you don\u0027t know then Blender/BforArtists with the .mu plugin. Import an existing BD Armory gun in and compare it to it\u0027s config file, to determine what needs to go where in the heirachy and then create your own. Simplest would be to 3d edit each section of the original model to what you want it to look like and save it as a new model.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUse my thread to get yourself started.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 dat